{"tid":41100,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴禾密友：佢寧願返巴塞做後備","createTime":"2016-12-15T15:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T09:31:59.000Z","uid":31314,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8170c66361be8ef32f48f66247d39fb85679bc3a","tid":41100,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:48:43.000Z","msg":"前巴塞門將巴禾在英超的經歷完全可以用「噩夢」來形容，加盟哥迪奧拿麾下的曼城之後，這位智利門神幾乎成為了藍月亮軍團的「大漏洞」，各至英超球隊都把他的弱點研究得透透的，屢屢成為球隊慘敗的罪魁禍首，巴禾感受到了英超的無比壓力。<br />\n<br />\n　　來自西班牙《金球先生》的消息透露，<span style=\"color: red;\">如今的巴禾在英超過得「非常不開心」，他甚至已經後悔自己當初加盟曼城的決定，該媒體稱，巴禾已經告知自己的朋友，他希望能夠回到巴塞效力，就算是擔任達史特根的後備也要回去。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　《金球先生》稱，巴禾至今沒有開始學英語，<span style=\"color: red;\">他根本不適應英超的節奏，而且極度討厭曼徹斯特陰冷的天氣。「他的自信和自負讓他離開了巴塞隆拿，但這是一個讓他後悔了幾個星期的決定。</span>」一位知情人透露說。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">辣殺</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec2579949a757958347564065dfb6010fa4b43c","tid":41100,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc32e0222cae77dd4a032b9fad889e3295c383e2","tid":41100,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:54:04.000Z","msg":"廢龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f4bacc84fb1360da9eebaeaae0a5cca0eba635","tid":41100,"uid":57049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"識控球在腳嘅巴禾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359379cbb98f7234ba6b0c8d22f8e0c7cdd7df51","tid":41100,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:56:51.000Z","msg":"懦夫"},{"pid":"adf209278508